==特色==
[[File:Citi_Field_Home_Run_Apple.JPG|thumb]]
紐約市有『[[大蘋果|大蘋果]]』的暱稱，當大都會球員擊出全壘打時，一個印有隊徽的巨大蘋果模型便會從中外野升起<ref>{{cite news|title=Two MN Companies Keep Baseball Tradition Alive|url=http://www.keyc.com/node/16362|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124022741/http://keyc.com/node/16362|dead-url=yes|archive-date=January 24, 2009|work=KEYC-TV News|date=January 20, 2009|accessdate=October 6, 2009}}</ref>，這項特色是延續謝亞球場時期的傳統。

花旗球場本壘後方的主要入口，球團規劃了[[傑基·羅賓森|傑基·羅賓森]]中庭（Jackie Robinson Rotunda）以紀念這位對大聯盟有重要意義的選手<ref name="Lupica">{{cite book|last=Lupica|first=Matt|title=The Baseball Stadium Insider: A Comprehensive Dissection of All Thirty Ballparks, the Legendary Players, and the Memorable Moments|date=2012|publisher=iUniverse|location=United States|isbn=9781462083664|pages=480}}</ref>；同時，花旗球場也規劃了名人堂，表彰曾為大都會隊貢獻的人物，大都會的吉祥物[[大都會先生|大都會先生]]（Mr. Mets）也是要角之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%B4%E8%A8%986-%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E5%8C%96%E8%BA%AB%E7%82%BA%E6%B4%BB%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90-mlb%E6%A3%92%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%87%B7%E8%88%8A%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85-190331384.html |title=運動產業王國側記6》球場化身為活教材 MLB棒球場的懷舊之旅 |accessdate=2019-05-26 |archive-date=2019-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526140319/https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2581%25B4%25E8%25A8%25986-%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%258C%2596%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259D%2590-mlb%25E6%25A3%2592%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2587%25B7%25E8%2588%258A%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2597%2585-190331384.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|publisher=New York Mets|date=April 1, 2010|title=Mets Hall of Fame & Museum opens this Monday, April 5, Opening Day at Citi Field|url=http://newyork.mets.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20100401&content_id=9041358&vkey=pr_nym&fext=.jsp&c_id=nym|accessdate=April 2, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615132939/http://newyork.mets.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20100401&content_id=9041358&vkey=pr_nym&fext=.jsp&c_id=nym|archive-date=June 15, 2011|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref>。

